<h1 class="doc-page-title">Data models</h1>
<p class="doc-page-lead">Technical documentation of COMPASS data structures, relationships, and entity models.</p>

<h2 id="overview">Data model overview</h2>
                
                <p>COMPASS uses a relational data model built on Entity Framework Core. The schema is organised into several logical groups:</p>

                <div class="row mt-4">
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h3 class="h6"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-primary"></i> RAID entities</h3>
                                <p class="small">Core entities for risks, actions, issues, decisions, and milestones.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h3 class="h6"><i class="fas fa-chart-line text-success"></i> Reporting entities</h3>
                                <p class="small">Operational reports, enterprise metrics, and functional standards assessments.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h3 class="h6"><i class="fas fa-cog text-info"></i> Administration entities</h3>
                                <p class="small">Users, settings, lookup tables, and system configuration.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h3 class="h6"><i class="fas fa-link text-warning"></i> Junction entities</h3>
                                <p class="small">Many-to-many relationship tables linking RAID items together.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h2 id="raid">RAID entities</h2>
                
                <h3 class="h5 mt-4">Risk entity</h3>
                <p>Stores information about identified risks.</p>

                <table class="table table-bordered table-sm">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Property</th>
                            <th>Type</th>
                            <th>Description</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>Id</code></td>
                            <td>int</td>
                            <td>Primary key, auto-incremented</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>Title</code></td>
                            <td>string(200)</td>
                            <td>Risk title (required)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>Description</code></td>
                            <td>text</td>
                            <td>Detailed risk description</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>FipsId</code></td>
                            <td>string(50)</td>
                            <td>Associated FIPS product ID</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>ObjectiveId</code></td>
                            <td>int?</td>
                            <td>Foreign key to Objective entity</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>RiskTierId</code></td>
                            <td>int?</td>
                            <td>Foreign key to RiskTier entity</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>Category</code></td>
                            <td>string(100)</td>
                            <td>Risk category classification</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>BusinessArea</code></td>
                            <td>string(100)</td>
                            <td>Associated business area</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>OwnerEmail</code></td>
                            <td>string(255)</td>
                            <td>Risk owner's email address</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>ImpactRating</code></td>
                            <td>int</td>
                            <td>Impact score (1-5, required)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>LikelihoodRating</code></td>
                            <td>int</td>
                            <td>Likelihood score (1-5, required)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>RiskScore</code></td>
                            <td>int</td>
                            <td>Calculated: Impact × Likelihood</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>ResidualImpact</code></td>
                            <td>int?</td>
                            <td>Impact after mitigation (1-5)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>ResidualLikelihood</code></td>
                            <td>int?</td>
                            <td>Likelihood after mitigation (1-5)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>Response</code></td>
                            <td>string(20)</td>
                            <td>Risk response strategy</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>ProximityDate</code></td>
                            <td>DateTime?</td>
                            <td>When the risk might occur</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>TargetDate</code></td>
                            <td>DateTime?</td>
                            <td>Target mitigation completion date</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>Status</code></td>
                            <td>string(20)</td>
                            <td>Current status (required)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>ClosedDate</code></td>
                            <td>DateTime?</td>
                            <td>When the risk was closed</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>Notes</code></td>
                            <td>text</td>
                            <td>Additional notes</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>IsDeleted</code></td>
                            <td>bool</td>
                            <td>Soft delete flag</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>CreatedAt</code></td>
                            <td>DateTime</td>
                            <td>Creation timestamp</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><code>UpdatedAt</code></td>
                            <td>DateTime</td>
                            <td>Last update timestamp</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <h4 class="h6 mt-3">Risk navigation properties:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><code>Objective</code> - Associated strategic objective</li>
                    <li><code>RiskTier</code> - Associated risk tier (single selection)</li>
                    <li><code>RiskRiskTypes</code> - Collection of risk type associations (many-to-many via junction table)</li>
                    <li><code>RiskActions</code> - Collection of associated actions</li>
                    <li><code>MilestoneRisks</code> - Collection of milestone associations</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="alert alert-info mt-3">
                    <p class="mb-0"><strong>Multi-dimensional classification:</strong> Risks can be classified by strategic objective, product (FipsId), business area, multiple risk types, risk tier, and custom category for comprehensive reporting.</p>
                </div>

